title: Ep.19: NFL Playoff Edition! Cowboys Last Play, Deebo, How Far Can Burrow Take The Bengals, Key Matchups, and Much More
description: In this episode we do a recap of every wildcard game and breakdown the good and the bad of every game. We also predict and bet on the upcoming playoff matchups.
